  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003carticle id=\"post-404064\"\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" width=\"1088\" height=\"612\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\" alt=\"New PS5 System Software update features audio focus and the return of the classic console UI customizations\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=1 1088w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.99 1077w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 816w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.61 664w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.49 533w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.41 446w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.32 348w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/77e0d1b0b7855d25e3981836025b2cbeb905e364.jpg?resize=1088%2C612\u0026amp;crop_strategy=smart\u0026amp;zoom=0.25 272w\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWe continue to work behind the scenes to bring new enhancements to the PS5 experience, and today we are excited to announce two key additions based on player feedback – audio focus  and the return of the classic console designs for the PS5 UI.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe PS5 system update will roll out globally in a phased approach, starting April 24.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eHere are details of the new features:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAudio focus increases immersion by providing presets to amplify soft sounds to meet your hearing preferences, ensuring a clearer audio experience when using headphones or headsets. This feature supports broader accessibility in audio experiences.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003cdiv data-youtube-id=\"2mcxoinz9zM\" data-title=\"\"\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\n\t\t\u003cimg src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/default.jpg 120w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/mqdefault.jpg 320w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/hqdefault.jpg 480w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/sddefault.jpg 640w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/maxresdefault.jpg 1280w\" data-sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\" data-src=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/maxresdefault.jpg\" alt=\"New PS5 System Software update features audio focus and the return of the classic console UI customizations\" srcset=\"https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/default.jpg 120w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/mqdefault.jpg 320w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/hqdefault.jpg 480w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/sddefault.jpg 640w, https://img.youtube.com/vi/2mcxoinz9zM/maxresdefault.jpg 1280w\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen the audio focus setting is turned on, you can choose from a range of preset options which makes it easier to distinguish sounds like in-game character dialogue, subtle sound effects such as footsteps and rustling grass, as well as voices in party chats for a more immersive gaming experience.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e●  To enable audio focus, go to [Settings] \u0026gt; [Sound] \u0026gt; [Volume] \u0026gt; [Audio Focus]. This feature can also be accessed from the Control Center, so you can easily adjust the settings during gameplay.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e●  You can choose from four preset focus type options for which sounds to boost:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e      \u003cstrong\u003eBoost Low Pitch: \u003c/strong\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003eAmplify low-frequency sounds like roaring engines and rumbling noises.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e      \u003cstrong\u003eBoost Voices\u003c/strong\u003e: Amplify voice chats, character voices, and other middle-frequency sounds.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e      \u003cstrong\u003eBoost High Pitch:\u003c/strong\u003e Amplify high-frequency sounds like footsteps and metallic noises.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e      \u003cstrong\u003eBoost Quiet Sounds:\u003c/strong\u003e Amplify low-volume sounds in a wide range of frequencies.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e●  You can set the level of support for each preset type from three different levels (Weak, Medium, Strong).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e●  Additionally, you can also choose to adjust the level of support for the preset for Left / Right channels separately to meet your specific preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e●  The audio focus feature is available when using headphones connected via USB or analog jack. It is not supported for HDMI connections through TV, AV receivers or soundbars.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=1 1024w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.99 1014w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 768w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.61 625w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.49 502w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.41 420w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.32 328w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/de2ffcd9776115b7127b65c5526524b97baa8bfc.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.25 256w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1170px) 936px, (min-width: 960px) 80vw, 100vw\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/adcb166d6a8509cce9934f58bcf987045e9adc73.jpg?fit=1024%2C1024\" alt=\"PS5 UI screenshots showing audio focus settings menu\" srcset=\"https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/adcb166d6a8509cce9934f58bcf987045e9adc73.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=1 1024w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/adcb166d6a8509cce9934f58bcf987045e9adc73.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.99 1014w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/adcb166d6a8509cce9934f58bcf987045e9adc73.jpg?fit=1024%2C576\u0026amp;zoom=0.75 768w, https://blog.playstation.com/tachyon/2025/04/adcb166d6a8509cce9934f58bcf987045e9adc73.jpg?fit=1024%2C5